{"tid":1631403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"知道點樣分辨五毛同鬼！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:30.000Z","uid":114901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a50c4bcbb426d830a480c0df0cac27624528aa2","tid":1631403,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"五毛同鬼無論講咩都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n態度一定好差引人反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真手足不割不切但會友善提出改善空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家已經無牌可以出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偏偏用成本最低嘅招數 就令大家對罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地內鬥 天上面嘅手足望到會好傷心<br />\n<br />\n感激每個手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b4c595329249591c3306ae4ca49aa4d9306a86","tid":1631403,"uid":311275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e196162287a30180d1f39848ea576f498d0b80e","tid":1631403,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d85899623d1c7d161ea103ee982b9f9512a972fb","tid":1631403,"uid":329268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"咁加句利申「純粹討論」咪扼到你囉"},{"pid":"2719c3a3d5780642c7ff72660f5695635e3f1ba5","tid":1631403,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"推 真係見到好多好極端<br />\n呢D唔駛理/ 不推文回覆，由佢沉底<br />\n理性友善建議請大家聽聽啦<br />\n都要保持獨立思考判斷"},{"pid":"db72d6eed4876e00884c0ba349b540b7fdcda022","tid":1631403,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"自推一下 相信真手足會識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會火遮眼俾人帶到風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a246fe6f8e3d19981cab278ccae10276ebd1e2","tid":1631403,"uid":162711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"[五毛名單整合] [勿中政府詭計］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631352</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}